id: pm-7tsx
title: "Advanced relevance tuning (post-v0.1): cross-encoder reranking + query expansion"
description: PRD line 1677 defers advanced relevance tuning. Add opt-in cross-encoder reranking on hybrid top-N and LLM query expansion before embedding to improve recall/precision for agent queries on large corpora.
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 3
